      <scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520">
         <head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
         <p>Included are 933 engravings of American statesmen, including some broadsides, and 35 autographed letters.</p>
         <p>Lists of portrait subjects and of letters are available in the accession folder.</p>
      </scopecontent>
